'''Glow-lichen''' was phosphorescent [[Lichen/Legends|lichen]] used as lighting that grew in the [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|Coruscant underworld]]. The [[Yuuzhan Vong]] used a similar strain, also called glow lichen, to provide light in their older [[Koros-Strohna|worldships]] and other derelict areas.

